summary: This document contains location data related to a mobile number, indicating the estimated location based on AT&T's records. It highlights the confidence level of the data and cautions against using it for investigative purposes due to potential inaccuracies.
keyFacts: The mobile number was located on 2020-07-01.
The confidence level of the location data is 90.
The radius of the location estimate is 9545 meters.
The data source indicates the results are presented in decimal format for 4G.
